Why Do We Need Seq2Seq?

Normal RNN predicts one output for one input.

Example:

Movie Review

Good Movie
      │
      ▼
Positive

This is many-to-one.

But translation needs:

English Sentence
        │
        ▼
Tamil Sentence

Both are sequences.

Hence we use Seq2Seq.

